The paper focuses on developing a personalized assistive navigational system for visually impaired users, which involves machine learning techniques such as reinforcement learning and regression algorithms. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), Robotics (cs.RO), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Sound (cs.SD). However, since the paper primarily deals with the development of a personalized assistive navigational system, we believe that cs.HC and cs.RO are the most likely sub-categories. The other sub-categories are also relevant, but to a lesser extent.
